'''圣经博物馆'''（{{lang-nl|Bijbels Museum}}）是[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]的一个博物馆。

==收藏==
收藏[[圣经|圣经]]和其他犹太教和基督教的宗教物品，包括[[荷兰|荷兰]]印刷最古老的圣经（1477年代尔夫特圣经）<ref name="nyt">{{cite news   | last = Labalme  | first = Corinne  | title = What's Doing in Amsterdam  | publisher = [[New_York_Times|New York Times]]  | date = 2002-03-31
  | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0DEEDB153BF932A05750C0A9649C8B63&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=2  | accessdate = 2009-02-25}}</ref>和1637年荷兰语圣经第一版。还有[[库姆兰|库姆兰]]的[[死海古卷|死海古卷]]摹本，包含[[以赛亚书|以赛亚书]]。

该博物馆还收藏19世纪发现的古埃及考古文物：油灯、泥板、陶器和钱币碎片等，给人们古埃及人宗教生活的印象。<ref name="nyt"/>

这里还有古代犹太圣殿的模型，包括[[所罗门圣殿|所罗门圣殿]]和[[希律圣殿|希律圣殿]]的模型，以及19世纪的[[会幕|会幕]]模型，内有[[希伯来圣经|希伯来圣经]]描绘的[[约柜|约柜]]。展览的一部分被称为“儿童故事阁楼”，利用光和声音讲述圣经故事，场景包括埃及、耶路撒冷和旷野。<ref>{{cite book  | last = Staal  | first = Gert  | title = Asking Questions: 10 Years of Architectural Design at the Gerrit Rietveld Academy
  | publisher = 010 Publishers  | date = 2004  | location = Rotterdam  | page = 273  | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=V6RC-AAAl5oC  | isbn = 978-90-6450-531-7}}</ref>

==历史==
2009年，该博物馆得到荷兰的彩票运营商的资金支持，获得所谓的范诺德韦克宗教书籍藏品。<ref>{{cite web  | title = Drie ton voor aankoop Bijbels met zilverwerk  | publisher = IKON  | date = 2009-02-17  | url = http://www.ikonrtv.nl/kerknieuws/nieuws.asp?oId=14848  | accessdate = 2009-02-25  | archive-date = 2013-02-22  | archive-url = https://archive.today/20130222130851/http://www.ikonrtv.nl/kerknieuws/nieuws.asp?oId=14848  | dead-url = yes  }}</ref>

该博物馆成立于1852年，于2002年庆祝成立150周年，[[贝娅特丽克丝女王|贝娅特丽克丝女王]]出席<ref>{{cite web  | title = Beatrix aanwezig bij viering 150-jarig bestaan Bijbels Museum  | publisher = Nieuws.nl  | date = 2002-11-22  | url = http://binnenland.nieuws.nl/47352  | accessdate = 2009-02-25  | deadurl = yes  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110720102749/http://binnenland.nieuws.nl/47352  | archivedate = 2011-07-20  }}</ref>。部分由于受欢迎的临时展览及大规模修缮，2001年至2002年间，游客人数增加了40％，<ref>{{cite news  | title = Recordaantal bezoekers voor Bijbels Museum  | publisher = Friesch Dagblad  | date = 2003-01-08  | url = http://www.frieschdagblad.nl/index.asp?artID=9946  | accessdate = 2009-02-25  | archive-date = 2011-07-21  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110721073533/http://www.frieschdagblad.nl/index.asp?artID=9946  | dead-url = no  }}</ref> 2006年超过了47,000名。<ref>{{cite news  | title = 2006 recordjaar voor Bijbels Museum  | language = nl  | publisher = [[Brabants_Dagblad|Brabants Dagblad]]  | date = 2007-01-02  | url = http://www.brabantsdagblad.nl/laatstenieuws/article972373.ece  | accessdate = 2009-02-25  | archive-date = 2011-07-20  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110720103111/http://www.brabantsdagblad.nl/laatstenieuws/article972373.ece  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>

==建筑==
自1975年以来，该博物馆设于[[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]的[[绅士运河|绅士运河]]畔的两座历史建筑内。其中包括荷兰保存最完好的17世纪厨房。

